				Matrix Consulting Group Inc. provides a full range of disability management services, and consultations to employers across Canada. <strong>All Matrix Consultants are former Workers Compensation Board Employees with over 200 years of combined experience.</strong> Whatever disability management challenges you have, Matrix can help with effective, low-cost solutions.
