		<div class="sixteen columns zeRow">
			<h1>PURPOSE</h1>
			<p class="no-margin">Disability, whether due to injury or illness, impacts the family, the workplace and potentially the community. Matrix Consulting Group Inc. provides effective disability management consultation. We strive to reduce the ramifications of injury or illness by arranging the safe and timely return of the individual to the workforce.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="sixteen columns zeRow">
			<h1>ABOUT MATRIX</h1>
			<p>Matrix Consulting Group Inc. was formed in 1993 to help employers contain workers' compensation costs. In addition to providing services in all aspects of workers' compensation, we also offer disability management services for short term and long term disability plans.</p>
			<p>Our goal is to assist our client's ill or injured employees return to the workplace as soon as they are safely able to do so, leading to the retention of valued employees and spearheading a positive relationship between management, employees, unions and healthcare providers. An effective disability management program contributes to a winning organization, and leads to lower claims costs and reduced premiums.</p>
		</div>
